 The cells in those tissues can make changes, sure,

05:25.180 --> 05:26.860
 but it's our nervous system

05:26.860 --> 05:29.360
 that harbors this incredible ability

05:29.360 --> 05:34.360
 to direct its own changes in ways that we believe

05:34.860 --> 05:37.740
 or we're told will serve us better.

