 I'm a big believer in black coffee.

21:37.940 --> 21:39.500
 I just happen to like black coffee.

21:39.500 --> 21:40.740
 People have asked me about,

21:40.740 --> 21:42.140
 and I don't wanna name brand names here

21:42.140 --> 21:45.620
 about this type of coffee or that type of coffee

