 And I'm gonna discuss this much more in future episodes.

23:24.580 --> 23:27.260
 Generally, states of high alertness,

23:27.260 --> 23:29.060
 when we're very, very alert,

23:29.060 --> 23:32.360
 are great for strategy implementation.

