 which is something that's interesting and we'll get into.

24:47.060 --> 24:48.460
 But for me, for instance,

24:48.460 --> 24:51.220
 I get up, I'm not terribly alert first thing.

24:51.220 --> 24:53.380
 And so I try and just get my brain

24:53.380 --> 24:54.900
 and my thoughts organized.

